description: I found a fascinating park in Prague. It looked like a place from fairy tale. It was almost magical. In the most beautiful part of the park I found a young couple who were nice and open-minded. The guy had a pretty big cock but wasn´t willing to let me anywhere near it. I left them and kept looking. I decided to risk a little and I chased down a jogger. Thank god I try to stay in shape... He was a college student and didn´t have exactly rich social life. All he did was school, work, and jogging. And I was about to barge into his life with an offer that comes only once in the life time. He was worried but it´s hard to say no to 25 000. Especially when you are a student. We just had to find the right place...
title: Czech Hunter 281
